sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User
    participant HI as SearchHistory
    participant App as DakoppervlakteApp
    participant GEO as useGeocoding
    participant PD as usePolygonDrawing
    participant GC as google.maps.Geocoder
    participant Map as google.maps.Map

    User ->> HI: Clicks history entry
    HI ->> App: onRestore(search)
    activate App

    App ->> App: setAddress(search.address)
    App ->> App: setSaved(false), setSearchError('')
    App ->> PD: resetAll()

    Note over PD: Clears all polygons, markers,<br/>preview line from map

    App ->> GEO: geocodeAndNavigate(address, onComplete)
    activate GEO

    GEO ->> GEO: setSearching(true), setSearchError('')

    GEO ->> GC: geocode({ address: address + ', Belgium', region: 'BE' })
    activate GC
    GC -->> GEO: results[0].geometry.location
    deactivate GC

    GEO ->> Map: setCenter(location)
    GEO ->> Map: setZoom(20)
    GEO ->> GEO: setSearching(false)
    GEO -->> App: onComplete()
    deactivate GEO

    Note over App,PD: 500ms delay for map to settle

    App ->> PD: restorePolygons(search.polygons)
    activate PD

    loop For each PolygonData in search.polygons
        PD ->> Map: new google.maps.Polygon<br/>(path from saved data, editable: true)

        Note over PD: Attaches path edit listeners<br/>for live area recalculation

        PD ->> PD: Add PolygonEntry with saved<br/>id, label, area, heading, tilt
    end

    deactivate PD
    deactivate App
